    • Method Detail

      • buildForest

        public ClassificationRandomForest buildForest(int size)
        Starts the forest building process. Each tree is generated with the generator received in the constructor.

        After every tree is generated, IRFGeneratorObserver.classificationTreeConstructed(int, int, int) method is called on registered observers.

        Parameters:
        size - number of trees to build
        Returns:
        trained random forest model
